{
  "video_id": "sdLOIPyL9ws",
  "title": "Designing the Apartment in ‘Friends’",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 830.0,
      "end_time": 5400.0,
      "text": "John Shaffner designed the most famous New York City apartment of all time."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5418.0,
      "end_time": 7950.0,
      "text": "Except it only had three walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7950.0,
      "end_time": 9350.0,
      "text": "and no ceiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9350.0,
      "end_time": 10799.0,
      "text": "And it wasn't actually in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10800.0,
      "end_time": 13650.0,
      "text": "This is my apartment, and I like it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13650.0,
      "end_time": 16400.0,
      "text": "John Shaffner designed the set of Friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22890.0,
      "end_time": 24400.0,
      "text": "John is a production designer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24400.0,
      "end_time": 26520.0,
      "text": "and John has worked on a lot of shows."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26520.0,
      "end_time": 30290.0,
      "text": "I've done 44 series, and 68 pilots."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30290.0,
      "end_time": 32650.0,
      "text": "“Dharma and Greg,” “The Drew Carey Show,”"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32650.0,
      "end_time": 35310.0,
      "text": "“Two and a Half Men,” “Big Bang Theory.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35310.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "And most notably, “Friends.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41200.0,
      "end_time": 42600.0,
      "text": "When I get assigned a new show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42600.0,
      "end_time": 45560.0,
      "text": "I do what is called a sketch model in white paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45560.0,
      "end_time": 48550.0,
      "text": "And you hold it up and you close one eye, and you squint."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48550.0,
      "end_time": 51900.0,
      "text": "And you can see just what the camera is gonna see."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51900.0,
      "end_time": 52638.0,
      "text": "Hello."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52638.0,
      "end_time": 54690.0,
      "text": "When we were presenting “Friends,”"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54690.0,
      "end_time": 56590.0,
      "text": "I presented a white model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56600.0,
      "end_time": 58130.0,
      "text": "and the producer looked at it and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58130.0,
      "end_time": 59490.0,
      "text": "\"Well, now what are we going to do about color?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59490.0,
      "end_time": 60420.0,
      "text": "What do you want to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 60420.0,
      "end_time": 62614.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"I think we should paint the set purple.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62614.0,
      "end_time": 63669.0,
      "text": "- Ooh. - Uh oh."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 63670.0,
      "end_time": 65470.0,
      "text": "Everybody was really anxious about."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 65470.0,
      "end_time": 66700.0,
      "text": "Nobody like change."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 66700.0,
      "end_time": 69410.0,
      "text": "Until I painted the little model purple."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 69410.0,
      "end_time": 70503.0,
      "text": "It's purple!"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 70503.0,
      "end_time": 74159.0,
      "text": "Color's really important in terms of establishing the show identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74162.0,
      "end_time": 75870.0,
      "text": "- Hey, ooh, slow down!"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 75870.0,
      "end_time": 77310.0,
      "text": "When you switch to “Friends,”"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 77310.0,
      "end_time": 80000.0,
      "text": "you saw that it was purple, and you stayed tuned."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 82350.0,
      "end_time": 84550.0,
      "text": "One of the responsibilities of a production designer"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 84550.0,
      "end_time": 86625.0,
      "text": "is to look into the future, if you can."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 86626.0,
      "end_time": 87459.0,
      "text": "(screaming)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 87459.0,
      "end_time": 90380.0,
      "text": "We put a door all the way up this hallway"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 90380.0,
      "end_time": 92839.0,
      "text": "and we really didn't say where it went to."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 92840.0,
      "end_time": 96060.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Why don't we just wait and see where the stories take us?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96000.0,
      "end_time": 98700.0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, years into the show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 98700.0,
      "end_time": 99619.0,
      "text": "we've never seen this door open."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 99620.0,
      "end_time": 100800.0,
      "text": "I wasn't trying to open your closet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 100800.0,
      "end_time": 102450.0,
      "text": "I wasn't trying to open your closet, I swear!"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 102450.0,
      "end_time": 104800.0,
      "text": "They do an entire episode about"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 104800.0,
      "end_time": 106640.0,
      "text": "this was Monica's messy closet."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 106640.0,
      "end_time": 107909.0,
      "text": "Oh my God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 107909.0,
      "end_time": 109905.0,
      "text": "(laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 109905.0,
      "end_time": 112720.0,
      "text": "(gasps)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 113370.0,
      "end_time": 115610.0,
      "text": "I definitely think that the coffee house on Friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 115610.0,
      "end_time": 117560.0,
      "text": "sort of influenced our culture of where"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 117560.0,
      "end_time": 119869.0,
      "text": "people like to meet and hang around."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 119869.0,
      "end_time": 120730.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 120730.0,
      "end_time": 122910.0,
      "text": "And now, of course, 25 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 122910.0,
      "end_time": 124709.0,
      "text": "there's a coffee house on every corner."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 124709.0,
      "end_time": 128393.0,
      "text": "I'm surprised how many of them have overstuffed chairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 128393.0,
      "end_time": 130259.0,
      "text": "What am I going to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132630.0,
      "text": "In the pilot, the moment when Rachel"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 132630.0,
      "end_time": 134799.0,
      "text": "walks through the door in her wedding dress"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 134800.0,
      "end_time": 136390.0,
      "text": "is a pivotal moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 136390.0,
      "end_time": 139709.0,
      "text": "We made a decision to put the door up here on a diagonal."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 139710.0,
      "end_time": 142000.0,
      "text": "She walks, pow, through those doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 143830.0,
      "text": "and straight to the camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 143830.0,
      "end_time": 147960.0,
      "text": "and everybody had to, like, physically turn and look."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 147960.0,
      "end_time": 148793.0,
      "text": "This is everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 148793.0,
      "end_time": 151130.0,
      "text": "This is Chandler, and Phoebe, and Joey."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 151130.0,
      "end_time": 152930.0,
      "text": "And you remember my brother, Ross?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 152930.0,
      "end_time": 153784.0,
      "text": "Sure!"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 153784.0,
      "end_time": 154617.0,
      "text": "- Hey. - Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 154617.0,
      "end_time": 155829.0,
      "text": "Oh! (laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 155830.0,
      "end_time": 157790.0,
      "text": "Who knew that that was going to be the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 157790.0,
      "end_time": 161300.0,
      "text": "of 10 years of a number one show on television?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 164530.0,
      "end_time": 168580.0,
      "text": "Audiences relate to sitcoms because once you get"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 168580.0,
      "end_time": 171950.0,
      "text": "to know the characters, you become invested in their story."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 171950.0,
      "end_time": 175609.0,
      "text": "So it's easy to turn on and watch an episode of Friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 175610.0,
      "end_time": 178300.0,
      "text": "It's a comfort coming back to visit with these characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 178300.0,
      "end_time": 179890.0,
      "text": "and be with them for that half hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 179890.0,
      "end_time": 182000.0,
      "text": "I'm so lucky I got to design Friends."
    }
  ]
}